01:04:55,800 --> 01:04:57,923
(LAUGHTER FADES)

980
01:05:04,320 --> 01:05:07,251
(NO AUDIBLE DIALOGUE)

981
01:05:12,400 --> 01:05:14,921
(SCRAPING ON METAL)

982
01:05:59,480 --> 01:06:02,331
(WATCH TICKING)

983
01:06:19,600 --> 01:06:21,639
(AUDREY)
"I guess only in America...

984
01:06:21,640 --> 01:06:23,879
can a 24-year-old girl like me...

985
01:06:23,880 --> 01:06:27,368
own a house like this
in Beverly Hills."

986
01:06:30,880 --> 01:06:34,119
Thank you all very much.
You've done a wonderful job.

987
01:06:34,120 --> 01:06:37,039
Take an hour and a half
for lunch. Back at 3:00.

988
01:06:37,040 --> 01:06:39,319
Don't forget to sign
the Boston hotel list.

989
01:06:39,320 --> 01:06:41,522
(INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS)

990
01:07:04,360 --> 01:07:05,999
- Excuse me.
