991
01:07:06,000 --> 01:07:07,884
No, no. Nothing.

992
01:07:15,200 --> 01:07:20,088
- There's no use to panic till
we find out what it really is.
- Would you stop that?

993
01:07:22,040 --> 01:07:26,199
(MAN) Dr. Ballinger is looking at him now.
Ballinger is the best there is, Audrey.

994
01:07:26,200 --> 01:07:29,359
- Dr. Hyman, we just left him.
- About half an hour ago.

995
01:07:29,360 --> 01:07:31,439
- And he seemed fine.
- Just fine.

996
01:07:31,440 --> 01:07:35,479
Well, he called. He said he had
chest pains. His left arm was numb.

997
01:07:35,480 --> 01:07:39,162
(DR. HYMAN) I'm bewildered myself.
I checked him about a month ago.

998
01:07:40,920 --> 01:07:43,239
All right, who's in charge
of this all-important...

999
01:07:43,240 --> 01:07:45,839
million-dollar show that
Mr. Gideon keeps talking about?

1000
01:07:45,840 --> 01:07:47,639
(JONESY) I guess I am.

1001
01:07:47,640 --> 01:07:51,599
Mr. Gideon is having attacks of angina
that could lead to a massive coronary.

1002
01:07:51,600 --> 01:07:55,359
Ah, shit! I gotta get back.
I'm fine. What do doctors know?

1003
01:07:55,360 --> 01:07:58,119
About angina, just a little
more than show people.

1004
01:07:58,120 --> 01:08:02,079
If you want to leave, fine, but I
think you'll die. Can I see you?

1005
01:08:02,080 --> 01:08:03,930
(JOE) Dr. Hyman?

1006
01:08:06,440 --> 01:08:10,159
The pain is gone. Nothing wrong
with me a rewrite wouldn't cure.

1007
01:08:10,160 --> 01:08:13,399
- Couple of good jokes is what I need.
- You can't leave now.

1008
01:08:13,400 --> 01:08:16,919
- Yes, I can.
- Damn it, Joe!

1009
01:08:16,920 --> 01:08:19,879
Didn't you hear
what the doctor just said?

1010
01:08:19,880 --> 01:08:22,128
Please, stay.

1011
01:08:28,120 --> 01:08:30,479
Joey, I've been talking
to Dr. Ballinger...

1012
01:08:30,480 --> 01:08:34,519
Jonesy, wait a minute.
Let me talk to the star here.

1013
01:08:34,520 --> 01:08:38,079
If I stay, how much time
are we talking about?

1014
01:08:38,080 --> 01:08:40,759
At least two or three weeks.

1015
01:08:40,760 --> 01:08:42,879
You've got to be kidding!

1016
01:08:42,880 --> 01:08:44,919
I got a show to put on!

1017
01:08:44,920 --> 01:08:47,239
For chrissakes, will you
talk to these people?

1018
01:08:47,240 --> 01:08:49,319
They don't understand anything!

1019
01:08:49,320 --> 01:08:51,319
Oh, Jesus.

1020
01:08:51,320 --> 01:08:53,719
- What's wrong?
- Miss Collins.

1021
01:08:53,720 --> 01:08:55,359
- All right, easy.
- Damn it.

1022
01:08:55,360 --> 01:08:57,679
You guys are doing this to me.

1023
01:08:57,680 --> 01:08:59,959
I wasn't sick until I got here.

1024
01:08:59,960 --> 01:09:03,164
- What's wrong with him?
- It's exhaustion.

1025
01:09:06,480 --> 01:09:08,728
You're lying to me.

1026
01:09:09,640 --> 01:09:11,444
Yes.

1027
01:09:14,920 --> 01:09:18,479
(KATIE) Uh, no, I'm not a member
of his immediate family.

1028
01:09:18,480 --> 01:09:20,959
I'm, uh... I'm his girlfriend.

1029
01:09:20,960 --> 01:09:23,719
Well, could I leave a message
for him, please?

1030
01:09:23,720 --> 01:09:26,446
- (♪ UP-TEMPO)
- Could you tell him that... Hello?

1031
01:09:30,680 --> 01:09:32,879
(JONESY)
It was just simply exhaustion.

1032
01:09:32,880 --> 01:09:35,759
He just tried to do too much.

1033
01:09:35,760 --> 01:09:38,119
Anyway...

1034
01:09:38,120 --> 01:09:41,799
we've made a decision to postpone
the show for four months.

1035
01:09:41,800 --> 01:09:46,439
- The doctors assured us Joe will be fine.
- There goes my new apartment.

1036
01:09:46,440 --> 01:09:49,439
Therefore the show will
definitely be done. I promise.

1037
01:09:49,440 --> 01:09:51,679
(SCATTERED APPLAUSE)

1038
01:09:51,680 --> 01:09:54,839
Now, we're aware of the...

1039
01:09:54,840 --> 01:09:58,479
- financial burdens this might impose...
- I gave up a TV series.

1040
01:09:58,480 --> 01:10:00,879
- On some of you, and...
- What a dummy.

1041
01:10:00,880 --> 01:10:03,999
We're prepared to try to get you...

1042
