temporary jobs,
or even lend you money.

1043
01:10:07,800 --> 01:10:11,399
Jonesy, easy on the money,
easy on the money.

1044
01:10:11,400 --> 01:10:14,809
All right, Larry. All right, okay.

1045
01:10:15,680 --> 01:10:18,919
We don't have
a lot of cash available, but...

1046
01:10:18,920 --> 01:10:21,959
what I'd like to say to you is...

1047
01:10:21,960 --> 01:10:25,119
I... we...

1048
01:10:25,120 --> 01:10:27,359
think of you all as family.

1049
01:10:27,360 --> 01:10:29,239
- Bullshit.
- And we want to do...

1050
01:10:29,240 --> 01:10:31,599
everything we possibly can...

1051
01:10:31,600 --> 01:10:34,039
to keep you all together.

1052
01:10:34,040 --> 01:10:37,559
(AUDREY'S VOICE) I was with him last
night. Already he's much better.

1053
01:10:37,560 --> 01:10:39,919
- (MOUTHS WORDS)
- I just left him an hour ago.

1054
01:10:39,920 --> 01:10:42,519
